---
layout: base.njk
title: About
summary: "Domus Communis Foundation — a global constellation of nonprofits advancing data sovereignty, sovereign AI, and values-based technology for the common good."
bodyClass: article
---
<article class="about">
  <header class="essay-banner">
    <div class="essay-banner-bg"><img src="/assets/events/may-24/quartey-1.jpg" alt="DCF gathering in Rome"></div>
    <div class="essay-banner-inner">
      <p class="essay-kicker"><span class="essay-publication">About the Foundation</span></p>
      <h1 class="essay-title">A common home for human-centered technology</h1>
      <p class="essay-dek">A global constellation of nonprofits advancing data sovereignty, sovereign AI, and values-based technology for the common good — guided by Catholic Social Teaching, serving people of all faiths.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="ab-wrap">
    <p class="ab-lead">Domus Communis Foundation is a global constellation of nonprofits dedicated to developing solutions for data sovereignty, sovereign AI, values-based AI programming, and emerging cyber technology that serve humanity rather than the reverse.</p>
    <div class="ab-prose">
      <p>We build a "cyber commons" — a globally networked collaborative space where values-based technology development operates through shared resources, collective solutions, and mutual benefit.</p>
      <p>Guided by the values of Catholic Social Teaching while serving people of all faiths, we bridge and connect AI and technology actors, global civil society leaders, academia, Nobel Laureates, faith leaders, and institutions to shape a future where data sovereignty, sovereign AI, values-based AI programming, and emerging cyber technology serve humanity, peace, and human dignity.</p>
      <a class="ab-xlink" href="/initiatives/">Our work runs through eight interconnected strategic initiatives →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ab-wrap ab-section">
    <p class="ab-label">The Constellation</p>
    <h2 class="ab-h2">A network without a center</h2>
    <div class="ab-prose">
      <p>DCF is designed as a constellation of nonprofits across the Global North, South, East, and West — connecting experts, academics, researchers, governments and regulators, representatives of civil society and humanitarian organizations, alongside companies and interested individuals, to advance data sovereignty, sovereign AI, values-based AI programming, and emerging cyber technology solutions for the common good of humankind.</p>
      <p>The shared-resource model lets the network operate cost-effectively around the globe, pooling talent and technology to accelerate the mission and maximize impact. DCF's mission and design are inspired by the Catholic Church, and the constellation's network architecture provides a bridge to and across the globe — ensuring that the values of all societies and faiths are represented in building technology for the good of humankind and global unity, in service of integral peace.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ab-geo">
      <div class="ab-geo-row">
        <span class="ab-geo-label">Established</span>
        <span class="ab-geo-places"><span class="ab-geo-place">United States</span><span class="ab-geo-place">Hungary</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-geo-row ab-forming">
        <span class="ab-geo-label">In formation</span>
        <span class="ab-geo-places"><span class="ab-geo-place">Japan</span><span class="ab-geo-place">Italy</span><span class="ab-geo-place">Ghana</span><span class="ab-geo-place">UAE</span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ab-wrap ab-section">
    <p class="ab-label">Inspired by Catholic Social Teaching</p>
    <h2 class="ab-h2">Our guiding principles</h2>
    <p class="ab-note">While inspired by Catholic principles, DCF welcomes and serves people of all faiths and backgrounds.</p>
    <div class="ab-principles">
      <div class="ab-principle"><h3>Human Dignity</h3><p>Every person possesses inherent worth; technology must serve and protect this dignity.</p></div>
      <div class="ab-principle"><h3>Common Good</h3><p>Technology should benefit all of society, not just the privileged few.</p></div>
      <div class="ab-principle"><h3>Subsidiarity</h3><p>Decisions should be made at the most local level possible.</p></div>
      <div class="ab-principle"><h3>Solidarity</h3><p>Technology must foster interconnection and mutual support.</p></div>
      <div class="ab-principle"><h3>Preferential Option for the Poor</h3><p>Technology should bridge gaps, not widen them.</p></div>
      <div class="ab-principle"><h3>Care for Creation</h3><p>Sustainable innovation preserving the earth for future generations.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ab-wrap ab-section">
    <p class="ab-label">Leadership</p>
    <h2 class="ab-h2">The people behind the Foundation</h2>

    {% for grp in team %}{% if grp.group == "Spiritual Voices" %}{% for person in grp.people %}
    <div class="ab-patron">
      {% if person.photo %}<img src="{{ person.photo }}" alt="{{ person.name }}">{% endif %}
      <div>
        <p class="ab-patron-label">Spiritual Voice &amp; Patron</p>
        <p class="ab-patron-name">{{ person.name }}</p>
        {% if person.role %}<p class="ab-patron-role">{{ person.role }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if person.bio %}<p class="ab-patron-bio">{{ person.bio }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}

    {% for grp in team %}{% if grp.group != "Spiritual Voices" %}
    <div class="ab-tgroup">
      <h3 class="ab-tgroup-name">{{ grp.group }}</h3>
      {% if grp.group == "Our Donor Coordinators" %}
      <div class="ab-coord-grid">
        {% for person in grp.people %}
        <div class="ab-coord"><span class="ab-coord-nm">{{ person.name }}</span><span class="ab-coord-loc">{{ person.role }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% else %}
      <div class="ab-member-grid">
        {% for person in grp.people %}{% if person.name != "Cardinal Silvano Maria Tomasi" %}
        <div class="ab-member">
          {% if person.photo %}<img class="ab-avatar" src="{{ person.photo }}" alt="{{ person.name }}">{% else %}<div class="ab-avatar ab-avatar-initials">{{ person.initials }}</div>{% endif %}
          <p class="ab-member-name">{{ person.name }}</p>
          {% if person.role %}<p class="ab-member-role">{{ person.role }}</p>{% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}{% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}{% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="ab-wrap ab-section">
    <div class="ab-cta">
      <h2>Join our mission</h2>
      <p>Partner with us to ensure AI and technology serve humanity.</p>
      <div class="ab-cta-btns">
        <a class="ab-btn-solid" href="#">Get Involved</a>
        <a class="ab-btn-ghost" href="#">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
